<subSubSection id="83810992BB7DFFC3FF2EFD27FA38F899" pageId="8" pageNumber="215" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="CB245A19BB7DFFC3FF2EFD27FDF4FC89" blockId="8.[136,1452,734,1807]" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB7DFFC3FF2EFD27FF49FD6D" box="[136,250,735,760]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">Diagnosis</emphasis>
:—differs from the European 
<taxonomicName id="0C9B219ABB7DFFC3FDECFD27FD17FD6D" box="[586,676,735,760]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Butyriboletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="8" pageNumber="215" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="regiu">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB7DFFC3FDECFD27FD17FD6D" box="[586,676,735,760]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">B. regiu</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
s by the different phylogenetic position, the basidiomes bluing when bruised and the finely tomentose pileus.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CB245A19BB7DFFC3FF1BFCDEFF67FCF0" blockId="8.[136,1452,734,1807]" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB7DFFC3FF1BFCDEFE86FCD5" box="[189,309,806,832]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">Etymology</emphasis>
:—‘ 
<taxonomicName id="0C9B219ABB7DFFC3FEC4FCDFFE65FCD5" authorityName="L. Fan &amp; H. Y. Fu" authorityYear="2022" box="[354,470,807,832]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Butyriboletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="8" pageNumber="215" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="sinoregius">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB7DFFC3FEC4FCDFFE65FCD5" box="[354,470,807,832]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">sinoregius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’; 
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB7DFFC3FE54FCDFFD92FCD5" box="[498,545,807,832]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">sino</emphasis>
, means 
<collectingCountry id="B38C1A89BB7DFFC3FD22FCDEFD79FCD5" box="[644,714,806,832]" name="China" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">China</collectingCountry>
, ‘ 
<taxonomicName id="0C9B219ABB7DFFC3FD44FCDFFC94FCD5" box="[738,807,807,832]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Butyriboletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="8" pageNumber="215" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="regius">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB7DFFC3FD44FCDFFC94FCD5" box="[738,807,807,832]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">regius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’ refers to this new Chinese species being similar to 
<taxonomicName id="0C9B219ABB7DFFC3FA35FCDFFF7EFCF1" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Butyriboletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="8" pageNumber="215" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="regius">
<emphasis id="F9EF860BBB7DFFC3FA35FCDFFF7EFCF1" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="215">B. regius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
